SystemRequirements: Package 'bigsnpr' includes a few functions that wrap existing 
    software such as 'PLINK' <www.cog-genomics.org/plink2>. Functions are provided
    to download these software. Note that these external software might not work
    for some operating systems (e.g. 'PLINK' might not work on Solaris).
